\section{Large scale predictions for semi-magic nuclei}
\label{predictions}

We are now in position to present large scale predictions of halo structures in mid-mass nuclei based on the one EDF parametrization used throughout the present contribution. We restrict ourselves to even-even semi-magic nuclei, which translates into about $500$ nuclei~\cite{hilaire07,doba04b}.

